{
  "texts": [
    "As they explained:",
    "I am an editor for a journal, and about eight months ago, back in the summer, I received an article, and the math looked correct, but the writing was terrible.",
    "It was so bad I could not even send it out to review.",
    "And so I wrote back to the author and said, \"Please, work with a native English speaker to turn this paper into reasonable English.\"",
    "And the next day, the paper came back to me in flawless English."
  ]
}